title: 该国已被禁止登录
author: Ares_heizi
txt_content:
提示所在国家被禁止登录
插件是AuthMe
版本1.7.10
以下是配置文件：

Protection:
  enableProtection: false
  countries:
  - US
  - GB
  - CN
  enableAntiBot: false
  antiBotSensibility: 5
  antiBotDuration: 10
  countriesBlacklist:
  - A1


把A1删了就好了
但是我把A1删了重启会他会自动变回去
enableProtection: false默认就是false
怎么搞...

replies.author: 世予予
replies.txt_content: 提示: 作者被禁止或删除 内容自动屏蔽

replies.author: Ares_heizi
replies.txt_content: 然后我把CN填上去也没用

replies.author: sgoye
replies.txt_content: 你直接把CN删了就行，填个UK就行

replies.author: Ares_heizi
replies.txt_content: 同一个插件，从面板服搬到VPS就出这问题....WTF
